Note: ===================================================================
Note: PHP LEXER
Note: ===================================================================
Note: Tokenizes PHP source code into lexical tokens for parsing.
Note: Supports PHP 7+ syntax including namespaces, type hints, and modern features.
Note:
Note: Part of the Translation Translation System
Note: Location: compiler/middle/gungnir/hir/translation/frontends/php/php_lexer.runa
Note: ===================================================================

Import "stdlib/core/string.runa" as StringCore
Import "stdlib/collections/list.runa" as ListCore

